                "description": "This is the resource description"
            }

+ Response 200 (text/plain)

    + Header

            Location: clients/john124/description
            Expires: Sun, 08 Nov 2015 21:11:41 +0000
            Last-Modified: Thu, 04 Jun 2015 21:11:41 +0000
